text: What a find!! East Tackle!! Managed to get some lures that are difficult to source in the UK. Fantastic service, great prices, great cats too. Thanks Andrew you provide an excellent mail order experience. Would love to visit your shopâ€¦.pity that there are many miles between us.
Thoroughly enjoy coming to this shop with nice music and friendly store owner. With Andrew's help, I bought my first high end fishing rod! Thank you for your wonderful recommendation bro!

Nice tackle shop with a very good ambiance. They have most popular tackle brands and a huge assortment of soft plastics for you to choose from ranging from keitech, island anglers, cultiva and many more. They are also the authorised resellers for daiwa so you can find most daiwa parts and upgrade kits from SLP here. Definitely worth visiting!
Difficult to find parking. However the shopping experience was great. Every time i try to browse the rod, the house cat will demand attention. Best employee.

Eastackle has become by far my most favourite fishing tackle store. The owner is a great guy, excellent at communication, and very correct. You can find in this store items that are probably difficult to find elsewhere and with good prices. I am absolutely happy with their service and I highly recommend it to any angler that is looking for some high quality fishing tackle.
